sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant B as Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis
    participant W as Worker
    participant G as LLM API

    C->>B: POST /api/submissions
    B->>DB: Fetch question
    DB-->>B: Question record

    B->>DB: Insert submission
    B->>DB: Insert details
    B->>DB: Set status=processing

    B->>R: XADD grading:tasks
    B-->>C: 200 {submissionId}

    W->>R: XREADGROUP grading:tasks
    R-->>W: Task payload

    W->>G: Grade with rubric prompt
    G-->>W: Criteria scores + feedback

    W->>W: Calc score, snap to 0.5
    W->>R: XADD grading:results

    B->>R: XREADGROUP grading:results

    alt High confidence
        B->>DB: Set status=completed
    else Medium/low confidence
        B->>DB: Set status=review_pending
    end

    B->>DB: Store AI result
    B->>DB: Record skill score
    B->>DB: Update progress
